Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}這樣的話將永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:22.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}活在童年無憂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:29.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無論如何都想要告訴你
