Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:44.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}心中卻深知再也沒有「再見」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:48.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}人生地疏的小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:51.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}我們在此相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:58.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}不知何時 微風在身邊刮起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:04.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}但我並不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:07.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}我只能盡力去傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:14.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}每當迷茫 困惑 受傷之時
